    Scope and Contents
The Lincoln Sites Conference of September 28-30, 1979, was sponsored by Sangamon State University and the Illinois Humaniites Council.  The title was " Lincoln's Thought and Present: A  conference on Historical Site Interpretation." The records include working papers, correspondence, financial reports, programs and news clippings.  The correspondence includes letters to and from noted Lincoln scholar Stephen B. Oates.  
  
